    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and <strong>pepper strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Once softened, transfer the <strong>softened pepper</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>softened onion</strong> and set aside for later</p>",
