      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>Hungarian-style smoky soup base</strong> to a bring to a boil over a high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped basa, </strong>the <strong>reserved onion & pepper </strong>to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and once boiling, reduce to heat to medium and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through – this is your <strong>Hungarian-style smoky basa soup</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
